                Send, receive and exchange currencies anyday, anywhere, anytime at the tip of your fingers.
            </p>
            <button class="rounded-full bg-brand-primary-950 px-6 py-4 text-white font-semibold text-sm">
                <a
                    href="https://forms.banffpay.com/cofor/form/Waitlist/formperma/3gfkggPKGMa3U8H3OWpOE_DkdPXJLJgyBtHl91gVA4g"
